msg: On the fsfs-improvements branch:  Simplify FSFS verify_walker.

author: stefan2
msg: On the fsfs-improvements branch:  Drop the copyfrom_cache that we
keep around for each FSFS svn_fs_t.
With the DAG node caching in place, its benefit is marginal even
in case of a copyfrom_cache hit.  The cost of creating and filling
it unconditionally by far outweighs the gains.
(svn_fs_fs__paths_changed): drop the cache from the signature
svn_fs_fs__paths_changed): drop copyfrom_cache from signature and code
(fs_rev_root_data_t): collapse into / replace by its only member
